                        <p class="text-justify"><i class="fa fa-star"></i> 12th standard or equivalent examination: You must have passed the 12th examination of a 10+2 system from a recognized Central or State Board or its equivalent examination.</p>
                        <p class="text-justify"><i class="fa fa-star"></i> Score: You must have passed your 10+2 with an aggregate of 75% in Physics, Chemistry and Mathematics or Biology.</p>
