                        <p class="text-justify"><i class="fa fa-star"></i> Top rank holders: If you are a top ranker or a candidate with Rank 1 in Central or State Boards in India, you will be offered admission to the programme of your choice; irrespective of your score or rank in BITSAT (as long as you meet the above criteria).</p>
