                  <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header" role="tab" id="headingOne">
                      <h5 class="mb-0">
                        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion-3" href="#collapse-3-2" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne" class="d-block text-dark text-capitalize text-up-small font-weight-700">Exam Pattern for MHT-CET</a>
                      </h5>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapse-3-2" class="collapse hide" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingOne">
                      <div class="card-block padding-30px">
                        <p class="text-justify">MHT-CET consists of two papers:<br>Paper 1: Physics <br> Chemistry Paper 2: Mathematics <br> Paper 3: Biology (Botany and Zoology)</p>
                        <p class="text-justify"><i class="fa fa-globe"></i> Paper 1</p>
                        <p class="text-justify"><i class="fa fa-star"></i> Subjects: Physics and Chemistry</p>
                        <p class="text-justify"><i class="fa fa-star"></i> Duration: 90 minutes</p>
