                        <p class="text-justify"><i class="fa fa-star"></i> Subjects: Mathematics</p>
                        <p class="text-justify"><i class="fa fa-star"></i> Duration: 90 minutes</p>
                        <p class="text-justify"><i class="fa fa-star"></i> Questions: 50</p>
                        <p class="text-justify"><i class="fa fa-star"></i> Marking scheme: 2 mark for every correct answer</p>
                        <p class="text-justify"><i class="fa fa-star"></i> Negative marking: No negative marking</p>
                        <p class="text-justify"><i class="fa fa-globe"></i> Paper 3</p>
                        <p class="text-justify"><i class="fa fa-star"></i> Subjects: Biology (Botany and Zoology)</p>
                        <p class="text-justify"><i class="fa fa-star"></i> Duration: 90 minutes</p>
                        <p class="text-justify"><i class="fa fa-star"></i> Questions: 100 (50 Each)</p>
                        <p class="text-justify"><i class="fa fa-star"></i> Marking scheme: 1 mark for every correct answer</p>
                        <p class="text-justify"><i class="fa fa-star"></i> Negative marking: No negative marking</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
