                  <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header" role="tab" id="headingOne">
                      <h5 class="mb-0">
                        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion-3" href="#collapse-3-3" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne" class="d-block text-dark text-capitalize text-up-small font-weight-700">Eligibility criteria for MHT CET</a>
                      </h5>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapse-3-3" class="collapse hide" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingOne">
                      <div class="card-block padding-30px">
                        <p class="text-justify"><i class="fa fa-star"></i> Age: Minimum age requirement is 17 years on or before 31st December of the year of admission.</p>
                        <p class="text-justify"><i class="fa fa-star"></i> The age limit is 25 years for a general category candidate.</p>
                        <p class="text-justify"><i class="fa fa-star"></i> The age limit for SC and ST category student is 30 years.</p>
                        <p class="text-justify"><i class="fa fa-star"></i> Subjects: Compulsory subjects include Physics, Chemistry and Mathematics/Biology.</p>
                        <p class="text-justify"><i class="fa fa-star"></i> Score in 12th standard or equivalent examination: As a general category candidate, you must have scored a minimum of 50% in your 10+2 or equivalent examination.</p>
